title: Jason Ackerman, Founder Of Fresh Direct
description: Host Jessica Harris talks with Jason Ackerman, founder of Fresh Direct, an online grocer. Harris also talks with Jessamyn Rodriguez, founder of Hot Bread Kitchen.
